Detailed Description

Holds CPPI_P0_FIFO_Status register contents. This is not applicable for 2 port switch.

Field Documentation

Uint32 CSL_CPSW_CPPI_P0_FIFOSTATUS::p0TxPriActivePri0

Port 0 Transmit FIFO Priority Active for priority 0 Indicates whether the corresponding FIFO priority has one or more queued packets on it or not. note: for N=2 this field is always zero (there is no transmit FIFO).
